description: In this course you will learn NodeJs basics which covers creating a simple web server, how to handle files, send emails,creating and exporting modules.
In this course you will learn ExpressJs basics which covers creating a simple app server, how to render and routes pages, creating middleware.
In this course you will learn HTML5,CSS and PHP basics which covers learning HTML tags,creating simple website, design the website using CSS basics and leanr to manage the dynamic features using PHP
In this course you will learn about Relational and Non-Relational Database. You will learn MySQL & Mongodb queries and how to design a effective database with practical examples.
In this course you will get a brief introduction to AWS console. You will learn basics of S3 bucket and EC2 instances
In this course you will learn the syllabus equivalent to the syllabus of AWS Solution Architect Associate Exam.
Here you will learn basics of C++ and Java languages. Course will include learning of datatypes, identifiers, loops and conditional statements.
